<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help & Support - Morti Projects</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-deep: #0a1628;
            --bg-primary: #0f1d32;
            --bg-card: #142640;
            --bg-glass: rgba(15, 29, 50, 0.6);
            --border-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --border-glass-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            --accent: #1199fa;
            --accent-glow: rgba(17, 153, 250, 0.4);
            --accent-dim: rgba(17, 153, 250, 0.12);
            --accent-secondary: #009e7e;
            --accent-purple: #8b5cf6;
            --text-primary: #f0f4f8;
            --text-secondary: rgba(240, 244, 248, 0.7);
            --text-muted: rgba(240, 244, 248, 0.4);
            --radius: 16px;
            --radius-sm: 10px;
            --radius-pill: 50px;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: var(--bg-deep); color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

        .main { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }
        .page-title { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .page-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 40px; }

        .section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .section-title { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .section-title .icon { font-size: 1.4rem; }

        .card { background: var(--bg-glass); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }

        .step-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
        .step-card { background: var(--bg-glass); border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 20px; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
        .step-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-glass-hover); }
        .step-num { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .step-card h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text-primary); }
        .step-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }

        .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass); }
        .faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .faq-q { padding: 16px 0; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .faq-q:hover { color: var(--accent); }
        .faq-arrow { transition: transform 0.2s; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .faq-item.open .faq-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }
        .faq-a { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease; }
        .faq-item.open .faq-a { max-height: 500px; padding-bottom: 16px; }
        .faq-a p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.7; }

        .status-list { list-style: none; }
        .status-list li { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 0.88rem; }
        .status-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .status-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
        .status-label { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); }
        .status-desc { color: var(--text-secondary); }

        .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
        .contact-card { background: var(--bg-glass); border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px; text-align: center; }
        .contact-card .emoji { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
        .contact-card h4 { margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .contact-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .contact-card a { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .step-grid, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/customer-nav', { currentPage: 'help', user: user }) %>

    <main class="main">
        <h1 class="page-title">üìñ Help & Support</h1>
        <p class="page-sub">Everything you need to know about using Morti Projects.</p>

        <!-- How It Works -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">üîÑ</span> How It Works</h2>
            <div class="step-grid">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-num" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); color: #f59e0b;">1</div>
                    <h4>Start a Voice Session</h4>
                    <p>Click <strong>Start</strong> on any project to begin a conversation with our AI analyst. Just describe your business problem in plain language ‚Äî no technical knowledge needed.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-num" style="background: rgba(6,182,212,0.15); color: #06b6d4;">2</div>
                    <h4>Submit for Design</h4>
                    <p>When you've covered everything, click <strong>Submit for Design</strong>. Our team reviews your requirements and creates a detailed solution design.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-num" style="background: rgba(17,153,250,0.15); color: #1199fa;">3</div>
                    <h4>Review Your Design</h4>
                    <p>We'll send you a solution design written in plain language. Review it, answer any clarifying questions, and approve when you're happy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-num" style="background: rgba(139,92,246,0.15); color: #8b5cf6;">4</div>
                    <h4>Approve & Build</h4>
                    <p>Once the design is approved, you'll receive a proposal with pricing and timeline. Approve it and we build your automation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project Stages -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">üìä</span> Project Stages</h2>
            <div class="card">
                <ul class="status-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üÜï</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Getting Started</span><br><span class="status-desc">Project created but no voice session yet. Click Start to begin describing your requirements.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üéôÔ∏è</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">In Session</span><br><span class="status-desc">You've started a voice session. Continue the conversation until you've covered everything, then submit for design review.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üì§</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Submitted for Design</span><br><span class="status-desc">Your project is with our team. We're analysing your requirements and creating a solution design. This usually takes a few business days.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üìê</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Design Ready</span><br><span class="status-desc">Your solution design is ready for review. Read through it, answer any clarifying questions, and approve to proceed.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üí∞</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Proposal Ready</span><br><span class="status-desc">A proposal with pricing, timeline, and deliverables is ready. Review and approve to kick off the build.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">‚úÖ</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Approved</span><br><span class="status-desc">Your project is approved and being built. We'll send you regular progress updates.</span></div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Voice Sessions -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">üéôÔ∏è</span> Voice Sessions</h2>
            <div class="card">
                <ul class="status-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üí¨</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Talk naturally</span><br><span class="status-desc">Just describe your business problem in everyday language. No technical jargon needed ‚Äî our AI analyst will ask the right questions.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üìé</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Upload files</span><br><span class="status-desc">Attach documents, spreadsheets, screenshots, or mockups to give extra context. We'll analyse them alongside your conversation.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">‚è∏Ô∏è</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Pause anytime</span><br><span class="status-desc">Click "Hold AI" to pause the conversation. Use Save & Exit to come back later ‚Äî your progress is saved automatically.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">üîÑ</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Multiple sessions</span><br><span class="status-desc">You can have as many sessions as you need. Each one picks up where you left off. Take your time getting the requirements right.</span></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="status-icon">‚úèÔ∏è</span>
                        <div><span class="status-label">Edit requirements</span><br><span class="status-desc">After a session, you can view and edit the gathered requirements directly on your project page before submitting for design.</span></div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQs -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">‚ùì</span> Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        How long does the design process take?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Typically 2‚Äì5 business days depending on complexity. Simple automations may be faster. We'll notify you as soon as your design is ready.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        Can I change my requirements after submitting?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes ‚Äî you can start a new voice session at any time to add more detail. If your design is already in progress, we'll incorporate the changes.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        What kinds of things can Morti automate?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Almost any repetitive business process: invoice approvals, employee onboarding, report generation, lead routing, data syncing between systems, document workflows, and more. If you're doing it manually and it follows a pattern, we can probably automate it.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        Do I need technical knowledge?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Not at all. Just describe what you do now and what you'd like to happen instead. We handle all the technical details.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        How does billing work?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>There's a one-time build fee when your project is approved, then an ongoing monthly management fee to keep your automation running, monitored, and updated. You can view your billing details in your <a href="/profile" style="color:var(--accent);">Profile</a>.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        What if I'm not happy with the design?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>You can ask clarifying questions and request changes. The design is a conversation ‚Äî we'll iterate until you're satisfied before moving to the proposal stage.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        Can I share a project with my team?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñº</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes ‚Äî project sharing is available. Contact your admin to set up shared access for team members.</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">üì¨</span> Need More Help?</h2>
            <div class="contact-grid">
                <div class="contact-card">
                    <span class="emoji">üìß</span>
                    <h4>Email Support</h4>
                    <p>Get in touch with our team</p>
                    <a href="mailto:support@morti.com.au">support@morti.com.au</a>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-card">
                    <span class="emoji">üí°</span>
                    <h4>Feature Request</h4>
                    <p>Have an idea to improve Morti?</p>
                    <a href="/dashboard" style="color: var(--accent);">Submit feedback on Dashboard</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
